; Coverage for times.cc lines 789-796: weekday specifier in period

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/08 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Test3
    Expenses:Food    $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --period "every week"
23-Dec-31 - 24-Jan-06           Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-07 - 24-Jan-13           Expenses:Food                $20.00       $30.00
24-Jan-14 - 24-Jan-20           Expenses:Food                $30.00       $60.00
end test
